snippet.title: De De Pyaar De 2 - Official Trailer | Ajay Devgn, R. Madhavan, Rakul Preet, Meezaan Jafri | 14th Nov
snippet.description:
In De De Pyaar De 2, love faces its toughest test yet as Ashish visits Ayesha’s family home!
Will the age-gap romance win hearts or stir things up? With heart, humour and a whole lot of family madness, this Pyaar vs Parivaar clash promises a relatable, riotous ride for every kind of audience.

De De Pyaar De 2 is directed by Anshul Sharma, produced by T-Series’ Bhushan Kumar & Krishan Kumar, and Luv Films’ Luv Ranjan & Ankur Garg. The film is set to release in cinemas on 14th November 2025.

snippet.title: Send Help | Official Trailer | In Theaters Jan 30
snippet.description:
Rachel McAdams. Dylan O’Brien. SEND HELP.

Directed by Sam Raimi, only in theaters January 30, 2026.

20th Century Studios’ Send Help, the upcoming darkly comedic psychological thriller from genre-bending visionary director Sam Raimi (Spider-Man, The Evil Dead).

The all-original film stars Oscar® and Tony Award® nominated actress Rachel McAdams (Spotlight, Are You There God? It's Me, Margaret., Mean Girls), Dylan O’Brien (Twinless, Saturday Night), Edyll Ismail (La Brea), Dennis Haysbert (Far from Heaven), Xavier Samuel (Elvis), Chris Pang (Crazy Rich Asians), Thaneth Warakulnukroh (Thai Cave Rescue), and Emma Raimi (Happy Pills), and releases in theaters nationwide on January 30, 2026. 

Linda Liddle (Rachel McAdams) and Bradley Preston (Dylan O’Brien), two colleagues who find themselves stranded on a deserted island after they are the only survivors of a plane crash. On the island, they must overcome past grievances and work together to survive, but ultimately, it becomes an unsettling and darkly humorous battle of wills and wits to make it out alive. 

“I’ve always loved stories where interesting, dynamic characters are pushed to extremes,” says director Sam Raimi. “In our story, the power shifts create an escalating situation that’s brimming with unexpected turns and suspense.” 

Send Help is produced by Raimi and Zainab Azizi (65), executive produced by JJ Hook (The Amateur), and written by Damian Shannon & Mark Swift (Friday the 13th, Baywatch), with original music by Danny Elfman (The Nightmare Before Christmas, Batman).

snippet.title: TRAILER REACTION u.a. auf FRANKENSTEIN, Die My Love & The Carpenter's Son
snippet.description:
Jesus… Wir werfen einen Blick auf die ersten Bilder zu FRANKENSTEIN und inspizieren wie viel Guillermo del Toro denn drin steckt. Darüber hinaus rätseln Andi, Schlogger und Schröck noch über 100 NIGHTS OF HERO und über die Version, die YouTube uns zu NO OTHER CHOICE (auf den alle Drei ziemlich Lust haben) rausgerechnet hat. Noch mehr vermeintlich Rätselhaftes gibt es mit DIE, MY LOVE, den Daniel allerdings schon komplett als Film kennt, während LITTLE AMÉLIE OR THE CHARACTER OF RAIN alle Herzen erobert, bevor eine oder einer auch nur „Ui, der sieht ja schön aus“ ausgesprochen hat. Und mit THE CARPENTER'S SON erfahren wir endlich, wie es war, als Gottes Sohn erstmal mit Nicolas Cage als Ersatz- oder Stiefvater klar kommen musste, bevor er dann mit seinen Homies durch die Gegend gezogen ist, um Wunder zu vollbringen. Zumindest sieht es so aus, was uns schon ein wenig zum Lachen gebracht hat. Euch hoffentlich auch, weshalb wir Euch nun nur noch viel Spaß mit dieser neuen Folge TEASE ME wünschen. Best bald.

snippet.title: The Family Plan 2 — Official Trailer | Apple TV
snippet.description:
Deck the halls, dodge the bad guys. The Morgans are back for The Family Plan 2, this time in Europe. Streaming November 21. https://apple.co/_TheFamilyPlan2

Dan Morgan (Mark Wahlberg) is many things: a devoted husband, a loving father, a celebrated car salesman. He’s also a former assassin. And when his past catches up to his present, he’s forced to take his unsuspecting family (Michelle Monaghan, Zoe Colletti and Van Crosby) on a road trip unlike any other.

The Family Plan 2 is an Apple Original Film hailing from Skydance Media, the sequel to “The Family Plan” will be directed by Simon Cellan Jones. David Ellison, Dana Goldberg and Don Granger will produce for Skydance, alongside Wahlberg and Stephen Levinson through Municipal Pictures. John G. Scotti will executive produce along with Cellan Jones. David Coggeshall, the writer of the first movie, has returned to pen the sequel.

Pokémon-Legenden: Z-A erscheint am 16. Oktober für Switch 1 und 2 und geht endlich mal ein paar neue Wege: Richtige Nebenmissionen, Echtzeitgefechte und eine riesige Metropole zum Erkunden. Doch einen Umschwung gibt's mit diesem Spin-off trotzdem nicht.

Seit dem Wechsel auf die Switch leidet die Serie unter technischen Problemen - und das ändert sich auch mit Z-A nicht, im Gegenteil. Vielmehr werden die Schwächen beim überschaubaren Schauplatz umso deutlicher.

snippet.description:
EARN YOUR LEGACY.

The 2025 League of Legends World Championship marks a historic milestone, the 15-year anniversary of LoL Esports. Worlds is the pinnacle of competition, where the best teams from the LCK, LPL, LEC, LTA, and LCP face off for the ultimate title, the Summoner’s Cup.

For fifteen years, Worlds has been the stage that forged unforgettable moments, defined careers, inspired regions, and gave the best players in the world the chance to earn their legacy. Now, a new generation of legends will rise to write the next chapter.

Play-Ins: Oct 14
Swiss Stage: Oct 15–25
Knockout Stage: Oct 28–Nov 2
